_iune_garnet_ver01/data/sn83045377/00332897470/1945101001/0100.pdf", "segment_count": 6, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045377/1945-10-10/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}, "resources": [{"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/iune/batch_iune_garnet_ver01/data/sn83045377/00332897470/1945101001/0100.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:iune:batch_iune_garnet_ver01:data:sn83045377:00332897470:1945101001:0095/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/iune/batch_iune_garnet_ver01/data/sn83045377/00332897470/1945101001/0100.pdf", "segment_count": 6, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045377/1945-10-10/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/iune/batch_iune_garnet_ver01/data/sn83045377/00332897470/1945101001/0100.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045377/1945-10-10/ed-1/?sp=6"], "batch": ["iune_garnet_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/illinois/", "2/united states/illinois/cook county/", "3/united states/illinois/cook county/chicago/"], "contributor": ["university of illinois at urbana-champaign library, urbana, il"], "date": "1945-10-10", "dates": ["1945-10-10"], "description": ["A Yugoslav Weekly Devoted to the Interest of the Workers OFFICIAL ORGAN OF J S F and Its Educational Bureau NO 1986 THE RIGHT TO STRIKE RETURNS Now that the war is at an end the nostrike pledge so faithfully honored by most Americas workers is a dead issue And so workers all over the nation are striking There is reason for strikes Prices have advanced despite the pledge of our wartime president that the line would be held Overtime pay has stopped with the result that the takehome pay of that large number of people who worked in war industries has been greatly reduced People need higher hourly rates now if they are to be able to pay the cost of ordinary living But an even stronger argument for higher wage rates is presented by those people who take into consideration the effect of a shift from a war to a peace economy While the war was on the government was private industrys biggest customer as well as its banker It was war buying that made jobs In the immediate future however it must be private buying it And unless the workers have the money to spend they will"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-05-21T10:21:03.684Z", "group": ["ndnp/iune", "university-of-illinois-at-urbana-champaign-library-urbana-il-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83045377/1945-10-10/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:iune:batch_iune_garnet_ver01:data:sn83045377:00332897470:1945101001:0100/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=267&w=207", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:iune:batch_iune_garnet_ver01:data:sn83045377:00332897470:1945101001:0100/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=535&w=414", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:iune:batch_iune_garnet_ver01:data:sn83045377:00332897470:1945101001:0100/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1071&w=829", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/iune/batch_iune_garnet_ver01/data/sn83045377/00332897470/1945101001/0100.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["cook county", "united states", "chicago", "illinois"], "location_city": ["chicago"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["cook county"], "location_state": ["illinois"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["3", "4", "8", "0", "2", "7", "1", "9", "sn83045